-- UBS CEO's pay rises 21 pct to 10.73 mln Sfr
-- 
-- Fri Mar 14, 2014 02:12AM EDT
-- None



ZURICH, March 14 (Reuters) - UBS <UBSN.VX> paid Chief Executive Sergio Ermotti 10.73 million Swiss francs ($12.30 million) for 2013, a rise of 21 percent over the previous year.

Ermotti was pipped as UBS's highest earner by investment bank chief Andrea Orcel, who was paid 11.43 million francs.